$NetBSD: patch-configure,v 1.1 2024/04/07 17:50:23 ryoon Exp $

Sun audio support.

Enable PIC on NetBSD, even on i386, to avoid text relocations.

Fix install_name_dir on Darwin.

Do not use 'rsync'.

